tyle="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">down his narrow cage</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">can seldom see through</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">his bars of rage</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">his wings are clipped and</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">his feet are tied</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">so he opens his throat to sing.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">The caged bird sings</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">with fearful trill</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">of the things unknown</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">but longed for still</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">and his tune is heard</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">on the distant hill&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">for the caged bird</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">sings of freedom</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">The free bird thinks of another breeze</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">and the trade winds soft through the sighing trees</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">and the fat worms waiting on a dawn-bright lawn</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">and he names the sky his own.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">But a caged bird stands on the grave of dreams</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">his shadow shouts on a nightmare scream</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">his wings are clipped and his feet are tied</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">so he opens his throat to sing</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">The caged bird sings</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">with a fearful trill</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">of things unknown</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">but longed for still</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">and his tune is heard</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">on the distant hill</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">for the caged bird</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">sings of freedom.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '1', '1', '', '', '', '2014-05-06 05:09:27', '1', 0),
(33, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:2:"96";i:1;s:3:"153";}', 4, '"Hope" is the thing with feathers', 'hope-is-the-thing-with-feathers', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">&quot;Hope&quot; is the thing with feathers&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">That perches in the soul&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And sings the tune without the words&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And never stops&mdash;at all&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And sweetest&mdash;in the Gale&mdash;is heard&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And sore must be the storm&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">That could abash the little Bird</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">That kept so many warm&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I&#39;ve heard it in the chillest land&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And on the strangest Sea&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Yet, never, in Extremity,</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">It asked a crumb&mdash;of Me.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '1', '1', '', '', '', '2014-05-06 05:11:17', '1', 0);
INSERT INTO `poems` (`id`, `submitter_id`, `topic_id`, `author_id`, `poem_title`, `poem_slug`, `poem`, `popular`, `poem_of_day`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `created`, `status`, `views`) VALUES
(34, NULL, 'a:5:{i:0;s:2:"29";i:1;s:2:"58";i:2;s:2:"63";i:3;s:2:"89";i:4;s:2:"96";}', 4, '"Arcturus" is his other name', 'arcturus-is-his-other-name', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">&quot;Arcturus&quot; is his other name&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I&#39;d rather call him &quot;Star.&quot;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">It&#39;s very mean of Science</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">To go and interfere!</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I slew a worm the other day&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">A &quot;Savant&quot; passing by</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Murmured &quot;Resurgam&quot;&mdash;&quot;Centipede&quot;!&nbsp;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">&quot;Oh Lord&mdash;how frail are we&quot;!</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I pull a flower from the woods&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">A monster with a glass</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Computes the stamens in a breath&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And has her in a &quot;class&quot;!</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Whereas I took the Butterfly</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Aforetime in my hat&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">He sits erect in &quot;Cabinets&quot;&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">The Clover bells forgot.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">What once was &quot;Heaven&quot;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Is &quot;Zenith&quot; now&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Where I proposed to go</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">When Time&#39;s brief masquerade was done</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Is mapped and charted too.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">What if the poles should frisk about</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And stand upon their heads!</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I hope I&#39;m ready for &quot;the worst&quot;&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Whatever prank betides!</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Perhaps the &quot;Kingdom of Heaven&#39;s&quot; changed&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I hope the &quot;Children&quot; there Won&#39;t be &quot;new fashioned&quot; when I come&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And laugh at me&mdash;and stare&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">I hope the Father in the skies</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Will lift his little girl&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Old fashioned&mdash;naught&mdash;everything&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Over the stile of &quot;Pearl.&quot;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '1', '1', '', '', '', '2014-05-06 05:49:22', '1', 2),
(35, NULL, 'a:3:{i:0;s:2:"89";i:1;s:3:"111";i:2;s:3:"147";}', 1, '"Heaven" has different Signsto me', 'heaven-has-different-signsto-me', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">&quot;Heaven&quot; has different Signs&mdash;to me&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Sometimes, I think that Noon</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">Is but a symbol of the Place&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And when again, at Dawn,</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">A mighty look runs round the World</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">And settles in the Hills&mdash;</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;">An Awe if it should be like that</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21.006000518798828px;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-